latestIgtvVideos.caption:

But what exactly does it do? Let's have a look!

• one mask has the power of 1 whole essence bottle 
• This helps it penetrate 10 layers deep into the skin with ease
• the result? Radiant, hydrated, bright and glowy skin!

That's not all! The mask itself is thin and exceptionally breathable with close to no dripping off of the product! Can you really say no to this brilliant product now?
